title: The Roundheads, or The Good Old Cause

items: Competitors for the Crown , but Lambert is General of the Army .
Chairman of the Committee of Safety .
An Oliverian Commander , but honest , and a Cavelier in his heart .
A Royalist , a man of Honor , loves Lady Lambert .
His friend of the same Character in love with Lady Desbro .
Footmen Fidlers , and a Band of Loyal City Apprentices ▪
